headline: Democrats in tight races abandon Biden as approval numbers plummet
author: Naomi Lim
sentences: They will probably throw in a few pictures of Pelosi and AOC and other extremely unpopular Demon-Rats in those ads for good measure too!!
Against mandates, open the schools, ditch the masks, heck next thing they'll be for is closing the border and tax cuts.
They are going to make sure that biden is shown in every political ad they run attacking their Demon-Rat opponent.
Not only are they abandoning Biden and his clown car, they're acting like they are speakers at a Trump rally.
Hopefully they will be able to find pictures of the Demon-Rats posing with biden.
But if they can't, you will still see a picture of biden in every ad.
The Demon-Rat candidates may try to abandon Lyin' Joe biden.
But their Republican opponents sure aren't going to.
Well, at least until the second week of November.
